*{{cite book|last=Richardson|first=F.M.|last2=Hunt|first2=Sir Peter (Forward)|title=Fighting spirit: A study of psychological factors in war|publisher=Leo Cooper|location=London|year=1978|isbn=0850522366}}
*{{cite book|title=Official Names of the Battles and Other Engagements Fought by the Military Forces of the British Empire During the Great War, 1914-1919, and the Third Afghan War, 1919|publisher=The Naval &amp; Military Press|author=Great Britain Battles Nomenclature Committee (1919-1921)|year=1922, reprinted 1993|isbn=1897632061}}

