| ''[[Podoviridae]]'' || Non-enveloped, short noncontractile tail || Linear dsDNA || [[T7 phage]]
|-
 | rowspan=10 | Unassigned || ''[[Tectiviridae]]'' || Non-enveloped, isometric || Linear dsDNA
