      <text xml:space="preserve">{{pov|date=January 2011}}
{{Infobox artist
| name        = Berthe Morisot
| image       = Edouard Manet 040.jpg
| imagesize   = 250px
| caption     = [[Édouard Manet]], ''Berthe Morisot with a Bouquet of Violets'', 1872
| birthname   = Berthe Morisot
| birthdate   = {{birth date|1841|1|14|mf=y}}
| birth_place    = [[Bourges]], [[Cher (département)|Cher]], [[France]] 
| deathdate   = {{death date and age|1895|3|2|1841|1|14|mf=y}}
| deathplace  = [[Paris]]
